<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureBuffer.CubeMapFace" Title="CubeMapFace enumeration" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureBuffer">ITextureBuffer</PageRef> ->
    CubeMapFace
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>CubeMapFace</TypeRef> enumeration identifies one of the six faces of a cubemap texture. It is used by cubemap texture data upload and update methods to select the face being written.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <EnumMemberList>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="PositiveX">
        Selects the positive X cubemap face.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="NegativeX">
        Selects the negative X cubemap face.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="PositiveY">
        Selects the positive Y cubemap face.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="NegativeY">
        Selects the negative Y cubemap face.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="PositiveZ">
        Selects the positive Z cubemap face.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="NegativeZ">
        Selects the negative Z cubemap face.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
    </EnumMemberList>
  </Section>
